The '''mountains of Mac. Robertson Land''' are located in the region [[Mac. Robertson Land]], [[East Antarctica]], between 60° E and 73° E. This region is claimed by [[Australia]] as part of the [[Australian Antarctic Territory]]. The area is highly glaciated. The availability of reliable data for this region is limited, making the list incomplete and inaccurate. The highest peaks, including [[nunatak]]s and [[ice dome]]s, are listed below:
